Old English Inns are part of The Great British Pub Card. If you love getting lost in British history, you’ll love our Old English Inns. With 100 locations in the most beautiful parts of the country, we have a collection of some of England’s most historic pubs, inns and hotels. The Great British Pub Card is the leading pub gift card that can be redeemed against food, drink or accommodation in over 3000 locations nationwide. Including brands such as Chef & Brewer, Loch Fyne, Flaming Grill, Hungry Horse and many others. The Great British Pub Card is also available to purchase as a digital code, its flexible and offers a vast choice of food, drink or dining opportunities. Perfect for celebrating those special times with family, catching-up with friends or meeting with colleagues. For more information visit www.greatbritishpubcard.co.uk.